{{Top|leg}}
'''Anthracite''' was a substance that was used for [[Starship/Legends|starship]] fuel. It could be left in piles in the open. [[Nilash III]] was a known source of anthracite.<ref name="Knight Errant Gazetteer">{{SW|url=news/essential-atlas-extra-the-knight-errant-gazetter|text=Essential Atlas Extra: The Knight Errant Gazetteer|int=The Knight Errant Gazetteer}}</ref>

{{Science-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
[[Wikipedia:Anthracite|Anthracite]] is a type of hard, glossy coal that burns without much smoke.

